#: src/mathlib.c:1034
#, c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"* Notice: \"%s\" was selected, but you can only change to a\n"
"* different Intel MKL threading library by restarting xnec2c.\n"
"* \n"
"* However, you may continue to select any other Linear Algebra library\n"
"* without restart, including this same Intel MKL library.  All other\n"
"* Intel MKL threading libraries are disabled until restart because of an \n"
"* MKL limitation where the MKL threading library can only be dynamically\n"
"* linked only once per runtime.\n"
"* \n"
"* See Intel's documentation on mkl_set_threading_layer() for more detail.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"* Napomena: \"%s\" je odabran, ali možete promijeniti samo na\n"
"* drugu Intel MKL biblioteku dretvi ponovnim pokretanjem xnec2c.\n"
"* \n"
"* Međutim, možete nastaviti odabirati bilo koju drugu knjižnicu linearne "
"algebre\n"
"* bez ponovnog pokretanja, uključujući ovu istu Intel MKL knjižnicu.  Sve "
"ostale\n"
"* Intel MKL biblioteke dretvi su onemogućene do ponovnog pokretanja zbog\n"
"* MKL ograničenja gdje se biblioteka dretvi MKL može dinamički\n"
"* vezati samo jednom po pokrenutoj sesiji.\n"
"* \n"
"* Pogledajte Intelovu dokumentaciju o mkl_set_threading_layer() za više "
"detalja.\n"

